#            **Memvid v2** AI-memory CLI by Phan Memvid Inc.) — a
#            **single-file crash-safe AI-memory storage format**
#            (`.mv2` extension) that bundles the typed retrieval-
#            augmented-generation (RAG) primitives into one
#            portable container:  typed embedded SQLite + typed
#            BLAKE3-hashed typed write-ahead log + typed embedded
#            **Tantivy** lexical inverted index (covered separately
#            in this corpus) + typed embedded **HNSW** vector index
#            for typed approximate-nearest-neighbor search + typed
#            embedded LLM (typed Phi-3 or typed llama.cpp-loaded
#            GGUF) for typed local question-answering + typed
#            multi-format document extraction (PDF, DOCX, XLSX,
