#            `.mv2` file is a single binary file the operator
#            can `cp` to any machine and `memvid ask` against —
#            no separate database / index / model directory to
#            keep in sync.  The typed embeddings + typed LLM
#            inference layer is powered by the canonical pure-
#            Rust ML inference framework **candle** by Hugging
#            Face (with typed Metal / CUDA / Accelerate backend
