#       • vec-search <FILE>             vector similarity
#                                       search
#       • ask <FILE>                    RAG Q&A with synthesis
#       • audit <FILE>                  audit report with full
#                                       source provenance
#       • timeline <FILE>               time-range frame query
#       • when <FILE>                   resolve temporal phrase
#                                       (feature: temporal_track)
#
